WEBVTT

01:00:02.000 --> 01:00:02.039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>BEEP</font></b>

01:00:11.320 --> 01:00:12.280
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Hi,</font></b>

01:00:13.320 --> 01:00:14.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I'm Sarah.</font></b>

01:00:15.639 --> 01:00:17.800
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Doctor Sarah Mandl.</font></b>

01:00:18.840 --> 01:00:21.400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>And the thing to </font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>know about me is...</font></b>

01:00:24.639 --> 01:00:25.960
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I'm dead.</font></b>

01:00:26.239 --> 01:00:27.639
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Murdered.</font></b>

01:00:28.280 --> 01:00:31.320
<b><font color='#fed64e'>No no, don't weep </font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>for me though, mothers.</font></b>

01:00:31.519 --> 01:00:35.239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>There's no grand</font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>cosmic injustice here.</font></b>

01:00:35.760 --> 01:00:37.559
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Hand to heart.</font></b>

01:00:40.880 --> 01:00:42.440
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I made a right mess</font></b>

01:00:42.599 --> 01:00:44.079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>of my life.</font></b>

01:00:45.320 --> 01:00:46.320
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But,</font></b>

01:00:46.519 --> 01:00:48.239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I had a plan.</font></b>

01:00:49.119 --> 01:00:51.440
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Yep. Sure did.</font></b>

01:00:52.000 --> 01:00:54.360
<b><font color='#fed64e'>And it almost,</font></b>

01:00:54.519 --> 01:00:56.119
<b><font color='#fed64e'>almost</font></b>

01:00:56.400 --> 01:00:57.519
<b><font color='#fed64e'>worked out.</font></b>

01:00:58.920 --> 01:00:59.920
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But,</font></b>

01:01:00.400 --> 01:01:03.320
<b><font color='#fed64e'>if you want to </font></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>make the devil laugh,</font></b>

01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:05.559
<b><font color='#fed64e'>tell him your plans. </font></b>
